g purposes retargeting only uses anonymous information  from the merchantâs site achievementsedit criteo won the  web award for outstanding achievement in web development criteoâs client boden won the clickz connected marketing award  for âbest use of display advertisingâ for its personalized retargeting campaign implemented by criteo see alsoedit ad tracking dotomi rakuten website visitor tracking referencesedit  criteo labs opening ceremony criteo website criteo retrieved  january Â   online ad exec greg coleman lands at criteo as president  kara swisher  news  allthingsd allthingsd retrieved  march Â   httpwwwdigidaydailycomdatastorieswhygregcolemanbetonretargeting  criteo brings scale to display retargeting says ceo rudelle adexchanger news and views on datadriven digital advertising retrieved  march Â   criteo brings its personalized banner ads to us launches new pricing program  venturebeat  news  by nadia majid venturebeatcom retrieved  march Â   french retargeting company descends on silicon valley clickz retrieved  march Â   criteolabs opening ceremony criteo website criteo retrieved  january Â   avik das  september  french ad firm criteo files for  million us ipo reutersÂ   ppc  how targeted display can extend your influence imediaconnectioncom retrieved  march Â   httpwwwitventcomaggregatorsourcespage  a b httpwwwmediapostcompublicationsfaarticlesshowarticleartaidnid  cost per click cpc marketing terms retrieved  march Â   httpwwwcriteocomnewspressreleasescriteohelpsmarketersboostincrementalsaleswithdynamicemailretargeting  criteo helps marketers boost incremental sales with dynamic email retargeting prnewswire  may  retrieved  march Â   allison enright web advertising  criteo makes placing display ads doityourself  internet retailer internetretailercom retrieved  march Â   criteo brings its personalized banner ads to us launches new pricing program  venturebeat  news  by nadia majid venturebeatcom retrieved  march Â   here comes the french invasi