 round in march  coming from french private equity firm agf and elaia partners and m â¬ in a second round in january  led by index ventures the company displays over  billion banners per month but does not disclose the geographical breakdown for those banners in may  criteo raised a further  million of funding from bessemer venture partners bringing the total to  million wxp privacyedit in september  criteo began a campaign regarding the use of the popular retargeting and its impact on consumer privacy the campaign aimed to reassure consumers about personalized retargeting and datadriven marketing tactics the company denies it relies on personally identifiable information pii and doesnât track identifiable information no data is shared with advertisers or publishers and no thirdparty data used for targeting purposes retargeting only uses anonymous information  from the merchantâs site achievementsedit criteo won the  web award for outstanding achievement in web development criteoâs client boden won the clickz connected marketing award  for âbest use of display advertisingâ for its personalized retargeting campaign implemented by criteo see alsoedit ad tracking dotomi rakuten website visitor tracking referencesedit  criteo labs opening ceremony criteo website criteo retrieved  january Â   online ad exec greg coleman lands at criteo as president  kara swisher  news  allthingsd allthingsd retrieved  march Â   httpwwwdigidaydailycomdatastorieswhygregcolemanbetonretargeting  criteo brings scale to display retargeting says ceo rudelle adexchanger news and views on datadriven digital advertising retrieved  march Â   criteo brings its personalized banner ads to us launches new pricing program  venturebeat  news  by nadia majid venturebeatcom retrieved  march Â   french retargeting company descends on silicon valley clickz retrieved  march Â   criteolabs opening ceremony criteo website criteo retrieved  january Â   avik das  september  french ad firm criteo files 